WEBVTT

00:05.505 --> 00:09.605
I love you very very much, more than the whole world.

00:11.495 --> 00:14.765
...I think that when I love you, I love you in a big way.

00:17.039 --> 00:24.861
How tired I am of this unbearable distance between us, how I long for the toll of the recess bell.

00:27.797 --> 00:31.415
Yes I do. I love you, I love you, I love you, I love you.

00:33.609 --> 00:36.584
I don't want him in my heart. I want him here with me.

00:39.116 --> 00:42.188
I'm in love with you and I want you to pick me instead of him.

00:44.230 --> 00:46.170
...but yeah, he won my heart.

00:47.809 --> 00:51.385
Oh, I love you, my prince.

00:53.479 --> 00:55.649
Good. 'Cause I like you.

00:57.551 --> 00:58.611
I love you.

